{
  "texts": [
    "We employed the SciBERT within the PyTorch for training the SFR model, with the weights sourced from 'scibert_scivocab_uncased' on Hugging Face.",
    "The model was trained on a GPU with A5000-24G, with the dataset split into training, validation, and testing sets in a ratio of 8:1:1.",
    "In a preliminary experiment, we use {1e-4, 1e-5, 2e-5} as learning rate value and {4, 8, 16, 32} as batch size value.",
    "We obtain the best results with a learning rate of 1e-5 and a batch size of 16.",
    "Other hyper-parameters were finetuned according to the performance on validation datasets."
  ]
}